==Finnish==
===Adjective===

#''vittuuntunut'' 

A person experiencing [[vitutus]] 

Derived from [[vittu]].

===Comparative levels===

#''vittuuntuneempi'' "more deeply annoyed [than someone]". Seldom used but not uncommon

#''vittuuntunein'' "most deeply annoyed [in the group in question]". Really seldom used, almost extinct.

